course.subject: SCIE
course.name: Community Services Project: Wofoo Grace Nursing Home
course.description: The course is offered in two consecutive terms, such as Fall to Winter, Winter to Spring, or Spring to Summer. The course is in a form of a community project at a designated non-governmental organization (NGO) under the supervision of the School. Each project will consist of at least four elements, namely training workshops delivered by members at the host NGO, design, implementation and execution of the service-project as instructed by the host NGO. Approval from the course coordinator is needed prior to enrolling in the course. Graded PP, P or F.
